name: The Social Distance。
description: Saturday, March 14, 2020 at 3:05 PM, San Francisco, CA. Lockdown how now gone into effect and this road at this time would normally be filled with cars commuting. Myself and the 2 people also crossing, all a block apart. This was when I knew the virus was a scary thing we were going to deal with. [2688 × 4032]
